HEADWORD: nuclear-powered submarine
<hw>nuclear-powered submarine</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A submarine for
which the motive power comes from the energy generated by a nuclear
reactor. Same as <er>nuclear submarine</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

